**Is it worth it?**

For most contractors, absolutely. If you're missing calls while on the job site, losing leads to voicemail, or spending evenings returning calls instead of being with your family, our service typically pays for itself within the first few captured jobs. One missed call on a rebar project could easily be worth more than a full year of our service.

