2026-05-03 12:00:13,474  INFO      Hi Tim,

Great questions — I appreciate you being direct.

**Is it worth it?**
If you're missing even one or two calls a month that turn into jobs, you're likely losing more than our monthly fee. A single rebar job can be worth thousands. Our AI answers every call 24/7, captures the lead, and makes sure you never lose a job to a competitor who just happened to pick up faster.

**What makes us different?**
Most answering services give you a generic script and a message pad. We train our AI specifically on YOUR business — your services, your pricing, your service area, the questions your customers actually ask. It sounds like part of your team, not a call center.

**What exactly do we do for you?**
- Answer every call, day or night, weekends and holidays included
- Capture lead details and job info so you can follow up fast
- Recover missed calls automatically with text follow-ups
- Handle estimate requests and appointment scheduling (on our Growth and Pro plans)
- Send you summaries so you always know what's happening

For a rebar company, this means your phone is always covered when you're on a job site, in a meeting, or just trying to get through dinner without interruptions.

Want to see how it would actually work for your business? I'd be happy to walk you through a quick demo — no pressure, just a look under the hood.

Book a time here: calendly.com/resolvops/free-resolvops-demo

Or just reply with any other questions — happy to help.

The ResolvOps Team
